And because of that, it's stupid that his suit is full of soot after his fight against the huge fire breathing turtle... His forcefield should avoid such a damage. So, either his forcefield is garbage over this film, he was again nerfed, oooooor... Gunn knows shit and decided to pretend his suit is just indestructible, which isn't.

